refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public Yaf_DispatcherYaf_Dispatcher::autoRender
 boolflag



 Yaf_Dispatcher 将会在分发到来的请求后自动渲染，可以带 flag &true;
 调用此方法来阻止渲染。



    也可以在操作中简单的返回 &false; 来阻止动作的自动渲染

  &reftitle.examples;

   Yaf_Dispatcher::autoRender 示例


<?php
class IndexController extends Yaf_Controller_Abstract {
     /* init method will be called as soon as a controller is initialized */ 
     public function init() {
         if ($this->getRequest()->isXmlHttpRequest()) {
             //do not call render for ajax request
             //we will outpu a json string
             Yaf_Dispatcher::getInstance()->autoRender(FALSE);
         }
     } 

}
?>


